io.nem.symbol.core.utils

Class CircularStack<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.nem.symbol.core.utils.CircularStack<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Type of elements on the stack.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class CircularStack<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Circular stack is a last in first out buffer with fixed size that replace its oldest element if full. The removal order is inverse of insertion order. The iteration order is the same as insertion order. Note that implementation is not synchronized.
